body.name: JUMMICO 3-Piece Wooden Round Table & Chair Set, Space Saving Kitchen Breakfast Nook Wood Grain Tabletop with Metal Frame and Built-in Wine Rack for Kitchen, Dining Room (Walnut/Black)
features: 【Space-saving Design】3 Pieces two Chairs and Table Set is elegent for any compact space, the chairs can be tucked under the table when not in use. The back of the chair fits perfectly with the rounded edge of the table, saving half the space. Oval-like desktop design makes it easy to fit into any small space.

【Kitchen Table Set】Simple and modern design makes it perfect for any home decoration style. You can put them into kitchen room, dining room,breakfast nook, balcony or apartment，if you want to have a meal with your family or have a drink in your leisure time,it will be your best choose.

【Built-in Wine Rack】A built-in Wine Rack for wines, snacks, fruits and books is designed directly under the table to add storage space. The proper height design also allows you to have enough room for your legs to move freely when using it.

【Durable Metal Frame】The base and legs of this table and chair set are made of black powder-coated solid premium steel pipe, avoid it to rust and bend. The MDF Table Top is added with a smooth and waterproof laminated panel. This table and chair set has a strong load-bearing capacity and can meet your daily needs.

【Product Dimension】Overall dimension: 35.8"L x 28.9"W x 30.7"H. Seat dimension: 13.4"L x 13.4"W x 30.7"H. Table dimension: 31.5"L x 20.9"W x 29.6"H. Maximum load: 220 pounds. Installation requires attention to the front and rear position of the two feet

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 23, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice , sturdy table set. We love it!
reviews.reviewText: So much sturdier than I had thought.it’s the perfect size for our little cabin, and love the color! There is plenty of height to scoot under the table and have extra space from thighs to rack.It has metal inserts in stool seat so the screws were not going directly into wood so the screws tighten down very good. I ordered pads to put on seat, but not sure if we will need them. The directions were fine, though we found that if you put the back rest on (before you put the seat on) you can get the seat holes lined up better , because you need to have the legs where they cross,tightened down before you screw the seat on. Also it takes some wiggling and tugging to get the screws all lined up so you don’t strip them out, and make sure you have the legs crossed right so holes line up for back. It came with all the hardware plus one extra of each , for just in case. Also came with the 2 tools you need to put it together. A hex wrench and a little wrench. It took 2 of us (me just being a helping hand while hubby did the work;) less than 1 hour to put this together , it would have been 1/2 the time if We had did it when we had more light as it was pretty dark when we started. Shipping was fast , and I am thrilled!!)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great Product. A lot of troubleshooting.
reviews.reviewText: The instructions were easy to understand. However, it isn’t as detailed as other ones I’ve seen.The chairs were a bit tricky to build. It was wobbly at first but what I had to do was just tighten the screw and nut at the same time. I used the two tools provided in order to do that. The seat itself was also difficult. Getting all the screws lined up and in the right place was a challenge. But it worked out fine, it just takes a lot of patience.Nothing about the table was hard. It does wobble a little but all the legs touch the floor and the wobble isn’t too noticeable.Though it was time consuming trying to fit the parts together perfectly and involved a ton of troubleshooting. This product is sturdy, perfect for small spaces, and looks great.

reviews.reviewText: This 3-piece table set was perfect for what I had in mind for my in-home office space. It is sturdy and looks beautiful. I bought it in addition to my computer desk unit I already have and it accents it perfectly for somewhere else to sit if I don't sit at my desk. It came in Black wood which matches my desk set perfectly too. It was super easy to put together in no time flat. No complicated words, just "picture" instructions to follow and the parts and hardware were clearly labeled which I loved! I highly recommend if you want something like this set to fit into a small space. I rated 5 stars!!! I am very happy with this excellent purchase!
